Prerequisite<class 'str'>
Desc:<class 'str'>
desc: 'You can hold yourself as still as a statue, evading detection.',
Benefit<class 'str'>
Misc:<class 'str'>
Name:<class 'str'>
name: 'Stoic Pose',
Misc:<class 'str'>
Desc:<class 'str'>
desc: 'You can plumb the depths of your mystery to use your revelations more often.',
Prerequisite:<class 'str'>
Benefit:<class 'str'>
Special:<class 'str'>
Name:<class 'str'>
name: 'Abundant Revelations',
Normal:<class 'str'>
Misc:<class 'str'>
Desc:<class 'str'>
desc: 'You can make a second attempt at failed hexes.',
Prerequisite:<class 'str'>
Benefit:<class 'str'>
Name:<class 'str'>
name: 'Accursed Hex',
Prerequisites:<class 'str'>
Desc:<class 'str'>
desc: 'Your ranger traps are especially difficult to notice and avoid.',
Benefit:<class 'str'>
Misc:<class 'str'>
Name:<class 'str'>
name: 'Advanced Ranger Trap',
Desc:<class 'str'>
desc: 'Whether with biting remarks or hurtful words, you are adept at making creatures angry with you. Diplomacy : You fluster your enemy. For the next minute, the target takes a –2 penalty on all attacks rolls made against creatures other than you and has a 10% spell failure chance on all spells that do not target you or that have you within their area of effect. Intimidate : The creature flies into a rage. On its next turn, the target must attempt to make a melee attack against you, make a ranged attack against you, target you with a spell, or include you in the area of a spell. The effect ends if the creature is prevented from attacking you or attempting to do so would harm it (for example, if you are on the other side of a chasm or a wall of fire ). If it cannot attack you on its turn, you may make the check again as an immediate action to extend the effect for 1 round (but cannot extend it thereafter). The effect ends as soon as the creature attacks you. Once you have targeted a creature with this ability, you cannot target it again for 1 day.',
Benefit:<class 'str'>
Misc:<class 'str'>
Name:<class 'str'>
name: 'Antagonize',
Prerequisites:<class 'str'>
Desc:<class 'str'>
desc: 'You control the type of spellblight your critical hits give your opponent.',
Benefit:<class 'str'>
Misc:<class 'str'>
Name:<class 'str'>
name: 'Blighted Critical Mastery',
Desc:<class 'str'>
desc: 'You cause creatures to take extra damage when you affect them with a spell that has the acid or fire descriptor.',
Benefit:<class 'str'>
Misc:<class 'str'>
Name:<class 'str'>
name: 'Burning Spell (Metamagic)',
Prerequisites:<class 'str'>
Desc:<class 'str'>
desc: 'You draw upon your channel energy to enhance the protective ability of your shield and those of allies while they are adjacent to you.',
Benefit:<class 'str'>
Misc:<class 'str'>
Name:<class 'str'>
name: 'Channeled Shield Wall',
Desc:<class 'str'>
desc: 'You cause creatures to be disoriented when you affect them with a spell that has the sonic descriptor.',
Benefit:<class 'str'>
Misc:<class 'str'>
Name:<class 'str'>
name: 'Concussive Spell (Metamagic)',
Prerequisites:<class 'str'>
Desc:<class 'str'>
desc: 'Your magical creations are infused with divine power.',
Benefit:<class 'str'>
Misc:<class 'str'>
Name:<class 'str'>
name: 'Create Reliquary Arms and Shields',
Prerequisites:<class 'str'>
Desc:<class 'str'>
desc: 'You can condense a fraction of your bloodline's power into a powerful elixir. When a creature drinks a sanguine elixir, it can activate the bloodline power anytime before the end of its next turn, as if it had access to that bloodline power. A creature that drinks the elixir cannot gain the benefit if its character level does not equal or exceed the minimum level of the bloodline power. Any level-dependent effects use the character level of the creature that drinks the sanguine elixir, or your sorcerer level, whichever is lower. Drinking a sanguine elixir is just like drinking a potion. A sanguine elixir is treated as a magic item with your caster level. Sanguine elixirs are extremely unstable. They lose their potency 1 day after they are created.',
Benefit:<class 'str'>
Misc:<class 'str'>
Name:<class 'str'>
name: 'Create Sanguine Elixir',
Prerequisite:<class 'str'>
Desc:<class 'str'>
desc: 'You have trained your eidolon to protect you.',
Benefit:<class 'str'>
Misc:<class 'str'>
Name:<class 'str'>
name: 'Defending Eidolon',
Prerequisite:<class 'str'>
Desc:<class 'str'>
desc: 'Your ki is so strong that it can deny death.',
Benefit:<class 'str'>
Misc:<class 'str'>
Name:<class 'str'>
name: 'Deny Death',
Prerequisites:<class 'str'>
Desc:<class 'str'>
desc: 'You can detect the mystic specialty of a foe.',
Benefit:<class 'str'>
Misc:<class 'str'>
Name:<class 'str'>
name: 'Detect Expertise',
Prerequisites:<class 'str'>
Desc:<class 'str'>
desc: 'Your tumor familiar goes to any length to save your life. The familiar must be aware of the attack and able to react to it in order to use this ability, and it can only do this once per day—if it is denied its Dexterity bonus to AC, it can't use this ability. Since this effect would not normally allow the familiar to make a Reflex save for half damage, its improved evasion ability does not apply on this saving throw.',
Benefit:<class 'str'>
Misc:<class 'str'>
Name:<class 'str'>
name: 'Die for Your Master',
Prerequisites:<class 'str'>
Desc:<class 'str'>
desc: 'You can convert a spell to interfere with an enemy's attack.',
Benefit:<class 'str'>
Misc:<class 'str'>
Name:<class 'str'>
name: 'Divine Interference',
Normal:<class 'str'>
Prerequisites:<class 'str'>
Misc:<class 'str'>
Desc:<class 'str'>
desc: 'Those within your dragonbane aura gain the same protection that you do.',
Name:<class 'str'>
name: 'Dragonbane Aura',
Benefit:<class 'str'>
Desc:<class 'str'>
desc: 'You have learned how to release most, but not all, of a spell's potential when you cast it.',
Benefit:<class 'str'>
Misc:<class 'str'>
Name:<class 'str'>
name: 'Echoing Spell (Metamagic)',
Prerequisites:<class 'str'>
Desc:<class 'str'>
desc: 'You are descended from a long line of sorcerers, and some portion of their power flows in your veins.',
Benefit:<class 'str'>
Misc:<class 'str'>
Name:<class 'str'>
name: 'Eldritch Heritage',
Prerequisites:<class 'str'>
Misc:<class 'str'>
Desc:<class 'str'>
desc: 'You can create an ensemble of skilled and amateur performers to aid you in your performance.',
Name:<class 'str'>
name: 'Ensemble (Teamwork)',
Benefit:<class 'str'>
Special:<class 'str'>
Prerequisites:<class 'str'>
Misc:<class 'str'>
Desc:<class 'str'>
desc: 'Your familiar is different from others of its kind. If you gain a new familiar, your old familiar loses all evolutions, and you can select a new 1-point evolution for the new familiar.',
Name:<class 'str'>
name: 'Evolved Familiar',
Benefit:<class 'str'>
Special:<class 'str'>
Prerequisites:<class 'str'>
Desc:<class 'str'>
desc: 'You can use your knowledge of a creature's weaknesses to deliver a driving and relentless assault against it.',
Benefit:<class 'str'>
Misc:<class 'str'>
Name:<class 'str'>
name: 'Exploit Lore',
Prerequisite:<class 'str'>
Desc:<class 'str'>
desc: 'Your dedication knows no limit. Your wrath dies hard.',
Benefit:<class 'str'>
Misc:<class 'str'>
Name:<class 'str'>
name: 'Extended Bane',
Misc:<class 'str'>
Desc:<class 'str'>
desc: 'You have unlocked the secret of a new magus arcana.',
Prerequisite:<class 'str'>
Benefit:<class 'str'>
Special:<class 'str'>
Name:<class 'str'>
name: 'Extra Arcana',
Misc:<class 'str'>
Desc:<class 'str'>
desc: 'You have learned how to draw more power from your arcane pool.',
Prerequisite:<class 'str'>
Benefit:<class 'str'>
